data.description: Space and storage abound in the 5-bedroom Capri plan from LGI Homes. This gorgeous one-story home provides a true retreat for the largest of families. With more than enough space for entertaining the Capri showcases a spacious family room and covered back patio. The open chef-ready kitchen features an abundance of beautiful wood cabinets and granite countertops, as well as a sprawling kitchen island and energy-efficient appliances. Homeowners will love the private master suite with its large walk-in closet. The gorgeous community of Poinciana is conveniently located near the best shopping, dining and entertainment the area has to offer!
